{{DISPLAYTITLE:Secret of Mana/RAM Map}}
This page documents the RAM layout for '''[[Secret of Mana]]''' (US version).

==Overview==
Secret of Mana uses the standard SNES RAM areas:
* Work RAM (WRAM): $7e0000-$7fffff (128 KB)
* Save RAM (SRAM): $306000-$307fff (8 KB)

==Character Data==

===Character Offsets===
Each character has a 512-byte ($200) data block:
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Character !! RAM Address !! Notes
|-
| Hero (Randi) || $7ee000 || Player 1
|-
| Girl (Primm) || $7ee200 || Player 2/AI
|-
| Sprite (Popoi) || $7ee400 || Player 3/AI
|}

