==SRAM Layout==

===Save File Structure===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! SRAM Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $0000 || 2 || Save 1 checksum
|-
| $0002 || 2 || Save 1 checksum complement
|-
| $0004 || $7fc || Save 1 data
|-
| $0800 || 2 || Save 2 checksum
|-
| $0802 || 2 || Save 2 checksum complement
|-
| $0804 || $7fc || Save 2 data
|-
| $1000 || 2 || Save 3 checksum
|-
| ... || ... || ...
|}

Each save slot is $800 bytes (2048 bytes).

